---
title: Berbere Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous with Lemon Yoghurt
description: Rich North African spices, brown sugar and lemon combine to give chicken an irresistible flavour boost.
Perched on a bed of tender roast veggies and fluffy couscous, and topped with zesty lemon yoghurt, this has
something for everyone.
